 treatment descriptions, recovery timelines, surgical explanations, and all other health-related information, is for informational and educational purposes only and does not constitute medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Always seek the advice of a qualified healthcare professional with any questions you may have regarding a medical condition."}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary mt-8 mb-4","children":"2. No Doctor-Patient Relationship"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Using this website, submitting enquiry forms, or sending emails does not establish a doctor-patient relationship. A formal consultation and in-person or tele-consultation with Dr. Sumedh Magar or any member of the I-SPORT Medical Centre team is required before any medical assessment or treatment decisions are made."}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary mt-8 mb-4","children":"3. Accuracy of Information Provided by Users"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Users agree to provide accurate, current, and complete information when submitting forms, appointment requests, or contact inquiries. Providing false or misleading information may result in denial of service or delayed/incorrect medical guidance."}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary mt-8 mb-4","children":"4. Appointment Bookings"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Submitting an appointment request through this website does not guarantee a confirmed appointment. Appointments are subject to availability and will be confirmed by the clinic team via phone or email. We request at least 24 hours' notice for cancellations or rescheduling."}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary mt-8 mb-4","children":"5. Intellectual Property"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"All website content, including text, images, graphics, logos, article content, videos, and other materials, is the intellectual property of Sportsurgeon.in and I-SPORT Medical Centre unless ot